hello star .hello python'\n    >>> h\n    'hello sheen .hello python'\n    >>> h.count('hello')\n    2\n    >>> h.count('e')\n    4\n分离与拼接\nsplit:分离join:拼接\n    >>> date = \"2018/08/11\"\n    >>> date.split('/')\n    ['2018', '08', '11']\n    >>> type(date.split('/'))\n    <class 'list'>\n    >>>list=[\"1\",\"3\",\"5\",\"7\"]\n    >>>\"+\".join(list)    \n    '1+3+5+7'\n\n\n                ", "mainLikeNum": ["0 "], "mainBookmarkNum": "0"}